<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Deletion Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .logo {
            width: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #f0f3ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .highlight-box ul {
            padding: 0;
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        .highlight-box li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .highlight-box strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        .footer span {
            color: #f97316;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="Logo" class="logo">
        <h2>Hi Team,</h2>
        <p>A user has requested the deletion of their account. Below are the details of the request:</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <strong>User Details:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong>
                    <%= userName %>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong>
                    <%= userEmail %>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Phone Number:</strong>
                    <%= userPhone %>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p>Please process this request as per our standard procedure and ensure all necessary actions are taken.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <span>Sharadha</span> Stores
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>